===生活方式===
良好的未被污染饮用水供应和好的卫生设备对于降低肠胃炎的感染比例和临床病例是十分重要的。<ref name=M93/>同时，研究还发现，无论发达国家还是发展中国家，个人的一些方法（比如[[洗手|洗手]]），都至少能使肠胃炎的发生率或者患病率降低30%。<ref name=Tint10/>使用酒精凝胶清洗液效果更佳。<ref name=Tint10/> [[母乳餵養|哺乳]]是很重要的，作为一种对于卫生条件的提升是非常重要的，特别是在一些卫生条件很差的地区。<ref name=Web09/>母乳喂养既可以降低肠胃炎的发生率也可以缩短其持续时间。<ref name=EBMED2010/>与此同时，避免食物和水的污染也是（预防胃肠炎发生）有效的方法。<ref>{{cite web|title=Viral Gastroenteritis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/ncidod/dvrd/revb/gastro/faq.htm|work=Center for Disease Control and Prevention|accessdate=16 April 2012|date=February 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424073547/http://www.cdc.gov/ncidod/dvrd/revb/gastro/faq.htm|archivedate=2012年4月24日}}</ref>

===接种===
为了保证疫苗接种的效果和安全性，在2009年，世界卫生组织呼吁全球范围内对儿童实施[[轮状病毒|轮状病毒]]疫苗接种。<ref name=WHORota2009>{{cite journal|last=World Health Organization|title=Rotavirus vaccines: an update|journal=Weekly epidemiological record|volume=51–52|issue=84|pages=533–540|url=http://www.who.int/wer/2009/wer8451_52.pdf|accessdate=10 May 2012|date=December 2009|archive-date=2012-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120709034841/http://www.who.int/wer/2009/wer8451_52.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Sz2010>{{cite journal|last=Szajewska|first=H|coauthors=Dziechciarz, P|title=Gastrointestinal infections in the pediatric population.|journal=Current opinion in gastroenterology|date=2010 Jan|volume=26|issue=1|pages=36–44|pmid=19887936|doi=10.1097/MOG.0b013e328333d799}}</ref>两种商业疫苗已经面世，而且还有更多的正在开发。<ref name=WHORota2009/>在非洲和亚洲，这些疫苗的使用已经大大减少了婴儿<ref name=WHORota2009/> 患重病的几率，而且那些推行了国家免疫计划的国家在疾病发生率和严重程度上已经有了明显下降。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Giaquinto|first=C|coauthors=Dominiak-Felden G, Van Damme P, Myint TT, Maldonado YA, Spoulou V, Mast TC, Staat MA|title=Summary of effectiveness and impact of rotavirus vaccination with the oral pentavalent rotavirus vaccine: a systematic review of the experience in industrialized countries|journal=Human Vaccines|volume=7|series=7|pages=734–748|url=http://www.landesbioscience.com/journals/vaccines/article/15511/?nocache=1111012137|accessdate=10 May 2012|doi=10.4161/hv.7.7.15511|pmid=21734466|date=July 2011|archive-date=2013-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130217163038/http://www.landesbioscience.com/journals/vaccines/article/15511/?nocache=1111012137|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Jiang|first=V|coauthors=Jiang B, Tate J, Parashar UD, Patel MM|title=Performance of rotavirus vaccines in developed and developing countries|journal=Human Vaccines|volume=6|issue=7|pages=532–542|url=http://www.landesbioscience.com/journals/vaccines/article/11278/?nocache=531156378|accessdate=10 May 2012|pmid=20622508|date=July 2010|archive-date=2013-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130217163031/http://www.landesbioscience.com/journals/vaccines/article/11278/?nocache=531156378|dead-url=yes}}</ref>而且这些疫苗通过减少交叉传染也可以保护未接种疫苗的儿童。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Patel|first=MM|coauthors=Steele, D, Gentsch, JR, Wecker, J, Glass, RI, Parashar, UD|title=Real-world impact of rotavirus vaccination.|journal=The Pediatric Infectious Disease Journal|date=2011 Jan|volume=30|issue=1 Suppl|pages=S1-5|pmid=21183833|doi=10.1097/INF.0b013e3181fefa1f}}</ref>从2000年以来，轮状病毒疫苗接种工程在美国的开展已经大体减少了80%的腹泻病例。<ref name="CDC Rota">{{cite journal|last=US Center for Disease Control and Prevention|title=Delayed onset and diminished magnitude of rotavirus activity—United States, November 2007 – May 2008|journal=Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report|year=2008|volume=57|issue=25|pages=697–700|url=http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm5725a6.htm|accessdate=3 May 2012|archive-date=2012-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120608073201/http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm5725a6.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Reduction in rotavirus after vaccine introduction—United States, 2000–2009 |journal=MMWR Morb.Mortal.Wkly.Rep. |volume=58 |issue=41 |pages=1146–9 |pmid=19847149 |url=http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm5841a2.htm |date=October 2009 |access-date=2013-08-25 |archive-date=2009-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091031060444/http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm5841a2.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Tate|first=JE|coauthors=Cortese, MM, Payne, DC, Curns, AT, Yen, C, Esposito, DH, Cortes, JE, Lopman, BA, Patel, MM, Gentsch, JR, Parashar, UD|title=Uptake, impact, and effectiveness of rotavirus vaccination in the United States: review of the first 3 years of postlicensure data.|journal=The Pediatric Infectious Disease Journal|date=2011 Jan|volume=30|issue=1 Suppl|pages=S56-60|pmid=21183842|doi=10.1097/INF.0b013e3181fefdc0}}</ref>第一剂疫苗注射对象为6-15周大的婴儿。<ref name=Sz2010/>而[[霍乱菌苗|口服霍乱菌苗]]最近两年也已经证实其有效率达50-60%。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Sinclair|first=D|coauthors=Abba, K, Zaman, K, Qadri, F, Graves, PM|title=Oral vaccines for preventing cholera.|journal=Cochrane database of systematic reviews (Online)|date=2011-03-16|issue=3|pages=CD008603|pmid=21412922|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD008603.pub2}}</ref>

== 处理 ==
通常，肠胃炎是一个急性并带有自控力的疾病，且通常不需要药物治疗。<ref name=NICE2009/>当前更受青睐的，用于温和地缓解在那些轻微到中等[[脱水|脱水]]的方法是[[口服补液疗法|口服补液疗法]]（ORT）。<ref name=BMJ2007>{{cite journal|last=Elliott|first=EJ|title=Acute gastroenteritis in children.|journal=BMJ (Clinical research ed.)|date=2007-01-06|volume=334|issue=7583|pages=35–40|pmid=17204802|doi=10.1136/bmj.39036.406169.80|pmc=1764079}}</ref>[[灭吐灵|灭吐灵]]和/或[[枢复宁|枢复宁]]可能对一些孩子有用，<ref name="Alhashimi2009">{{cite journal |author=Alhashimi D, Al-Hashimi H, Fedorowicz Z|editor1-last=Alhashimi |editor1-first=Dunia |title=Antiemetics for reducing vomiting related to acute gastroenteritis in children and adolescents|journal=Cochrane Database Syst Rev |issue=2 |pages=CD005506 |year=2009 |pmid=19370620|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD005506.pub4 }}</ref>而[[丁基东莨菪碱|丁基东莨菪碱]]则可用于治疗[[腹痛|腹痛]]。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Tytgat GN |title=Hyoscine butylbromide: a review of its use in the treatment of abdominal cramping and pain |journal=Drugs |volume=67 |issue=9 |pages=1343–57 |year=2007 |pmid=17547475 }}</ref>

=== 补充水分 ===
对于儿童和成人肠胃炎的基本处理方法是[[水分補充|水分補充]]。而經口補水疗法的出现更好地实现了这一点，虽然当患者[[意识水平下降|意识水平下降]]或者脱水相当严重时，[[静脉注射治疗|静脉注射]]是必要的程序。但口服補水疗法仍是一种很好的補水方法。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bestbets.org/bets/bet.php?id=1039 |title=BestBets:Fluid Treatment of Gastroenteritis in Adults |accessdate=2013-08-25 |archive-date=2013-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130517013547/http://www.bestbets.org/bets/bet.php?id=1039 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Canavan A, Arant BS |title=Diagnosis and management of dehydration in children |journal=Am Fam Physician|volume=80 |issue=7 |pages=692–6 |pmid=19817339 |date=October 2009}}</ref>口服替代疗法产品之中，使用碳水化合物（即小麦或米）的食（飲）品优先於富含单糖的食（飲）品。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Gregorio GV, Gonzales ML, Dans LF, Martinez EG |editor1-last=Gregorio |editor1-first=Germana V |title=Polymer-based oral rehydration solution for treating acute watery diarrhoea |journal=Cochrane Database Syst Rev |issue=2 |pages=CD006519 |year=2009 |pmid=19370638 |doi=10.1002/14651858.CD006519.pub2}}</ref>富含单糖的饮料，例如[[汽水|汽水]]，果汁等，不建議给5岁以下的孩子使用，因为它们可能会加重腹泻。<ref name=NICE2009/>如果没有特效的口服补液剂或者味道较差，白开水也是可以使用的。<ref name=NICE2009/>如有适应症，亦可在儿童身上使用[[鼻胃管|鼻胃管]]来补充流质。<ref name=Webb2005/>

===膳食===
母乳喂养的婴儿建议以平时的喂养方法继续，配方奶喂养的婴儿在ORT补液后立即继续配方喂养。<ref name=MMWR2003/>通常不需要改为无乳糖或低乳糖配方。<ref name=MMWR2003/>发生腹泻时，儿童应进食与平常相同的饭食，但应避免高[[单糖|单糖]]的食物。<ref name=MMWR2003/>[[BRAT餐|BRAT餐]](香蕉、米饭、苹果酱、烤面包和茶）已不再是推荐饮食，因为它不包含足够的养分，并且相对平常饮食并无优点。<ref name=MMWR2003>{{cite journal |author=King CK, Glass R, Bresee JS, Duggan C |title=Managing acute gastroenteritis among children: oral rehydration, maintenance, and nutritional therapy |journal=MMWR Recomm Rep |volume=52 |issue=RR-16 |pages=1–16 |pmid=14627948 |url=http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/rr5216a1.htm |date=November 2003 |access-date=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2014-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028174056/http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/rr5216a1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>一些[[益生菌|益生菌]]已被证明有利于减少腹泻的延续时间和大便的次数，<ref>{{cite journal |author=Allen SJ, Martinez EG, Gregorio GV, Dans LF |editor1-last=Allen |editor1-first=Stephen J |title=Probiotics for treating acute infectious diarrhoea |journal=Cochrane Database Syst Rev |volume=11 |issue= 11|pages=CD003048 |year=2010 |pmid=21069673 |doi=10.1002/14651858.CD003048.pub3}}</ref>并且在预防和治疗[[抗生素相关性的腹泻|抗生素相关性的腹泻]]上也许有用。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Hempel|first=S|coauthors=Newberry, SJ; Maher, AR; Wang, Z; Miles, JN; Shanman, R; Johnsen, B; Shekelle, PG|title=Probiotics for the prevention and treatment of antibiotic-associated diarrhea: a systematic review and meta-analysis. |journal=JAMA : the journal of the American Medical Association|date=2012-05-09|volume=307|issue=18|pages=1959-69|pmid=22570464}}</ref>类似的，发酵的乳类产品（如 [[酸奶|酸奶]]）等也同样有益。<ref>{{cite web|last=Mackway-Jones|first=Kevin|title=Does yogurt decrease acute diarrhoeal symptoms in children with acute gastroenteritis?|url=http://www.bestbets.org/bets/bet.php?id=1000|work=BestBets|date=June 2007|accessdate=2016-11-04|archive-date=2013-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130517002703/http://www.bestbets.org/bets/bet.php?id=1000|dead-url=yes}}</ref>补[[锌|锌]]在发展中世界儿童腹泻的预防及治疗上似乎有效。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Telmesani|first=AM|title=Oral rehydration salts, zinc supplement and rota virus vaccine in the management of childhood acute diarrhea. |journal=Journal of family and community medicine|date=2010 May|volume=17|issue=2|pages=79–82|pmid=21359029|doi=10.4103/1319-1683.71988|pmc = 3045093}}</ref>

===止吐药===
[[止吐|止吐]]药物可能有助于治疗小儿呕吐。[[昂丹司琼|昂丹司琼]]有一定实用，单次使用即可减少静脉输液需求、住院需求及呕吐。<ref>{{cite journal |author=DeCamp LR, Byerley JS, Doshi N, Steiner MJ |title=Use of antiemetic agents in acute gastroenteritis: a systematic review and meta-analysis |journal=Arch Pediatr Adolesc Med|volume=162 |issue=9 |pages=858–65 |pmid=18762604|doi=10.1001/archpedi.162.9.858 |date=September 2008}}</ref><ref name="pmid17279195">{{cite journal| author = Mehta S, Goldman RD| title = Ondansetron for acute gastroenteritis in children| journal = Can Fam Physician| volume = 52| issue = 11| pages = 1397–8| year = 2006| pmid = 17279195| url = http://www.cfp.ca/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=17279195| pmc = 1783696| access-date = 2016-11-04| archive-date = 2020-05-30| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200530060338/https://www.cfp.ca/content/52/11/1397.long| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name=Cochrane2011/>[[胃复安|胃复安]]也可能有效。<ref name=Cochrane2011>{{cite journal|last=Fedorowicz|first=Z|coauthors=Jagannath, VA, Carter, B|title=Antiemetics for reducing vomiting related to acute gastroenteritis in children and adolescents. |journal=Cochrane database of systematic reviews (Online)|date=2011-09-07|volume=9|pages=CD005506|pmid=21901699|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD005506.pub5|issue=9}}</ref>但是昂但司琼的使用可能与小儿再次入院几率增加有关。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Sturm JJ, Hirsh DA, Schweickert A, Massey R, Simon HK|title=Ondansetron use in the pediatric emergency department and effects on hospitalization and return rates: are we masking alternative diagnoses?|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_annals-of-emergency-medicine_2010-05_55_5/page/415|journal=Ann Emerg Med |volume=55 |issue=5 |pages=415–22 |pmid=20031265 |doi=10.1016/j.annemergmed.2009.11.011 |date=May 2010}}</ref>如果临床上需要，昂丹司琼的静脉液也可以口服。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ondansetron|url=http://www.merckmanuals.com/professional/print/lexicomp/ondansetron.html|work=Lexi-Comp|date=May 2011|accessdate=2016-11-04|archive-date=2012-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120606132320/http://www.merckmanuals.com/professional/print/lexicomp/ondansetron.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[茶苯海明|茶苯海明]]虽然能减少呕吐，但临床效用似乎并不大。<ref name=EBMED2010/>

===抗生素===
抗生素通常不用在肠胃炎治療，但如果症状特别严重时<ref>{{cite journal |author=Traa BS, Walker CL, Munos M, Black RE |title=Antibiotics for the treatment of dysentery in children |journal=Int J Epidemiol|volume=39 |issue=Suppl 1 |pages=i70–4 |pmid=20348130 |pmc=2845863 |doi=10.1093/ije/dyq024|date=April 2010}}</ref>或在找到了易感细菌、怀疑某细菌感染的情况下是建议使用的。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Grimwood K, Forbes DA |title=Acute and persistent diarrhea |journal=Pediatr. Clin. North Am. |volume=56 |issue=6 |pages=1343–61 |pmid=19962025 |doi=10.1016/j.pcl.2009.09.004|date=December 2009}}</ref>如果要使用抗生素，则[[大环内酯类|大环内酯类]]（如[[阿奇霉素|阿奇霉素]]）优于[[氟喹诺酮类药物|氟喹诺酮类药物]]，因为后者抗药性较高。<ref name=Bact2007/>[[伪膜性肠炎|伪膜性肠炎]]通常由使用抗生素引起，治疗方法为中断病源及用[[甲硝唑|甲硝唑]]或[[万古霉素|万古霉素]]治疗。<ref name="Mandell"/>可治疗的细菌和原虫包括[[菌痢|志贺杆菌]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Christopher|first=PR|coauthors=David, KV, John, SM, Sankarapandian, V|title=Antibiotic therapy for Shigelladysentery. |journal=Cochrane database of systematic reviews (Online)|date=2010-08-04|issue=8|pages=CD006784|pmid=20687081|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD006784.pub4}}</ref> ''[[Salmonellosis|Salmonella typhi]]'',<ref>{{cite journal|last=Effa|first=EE|coauthors=Lassi, ZS, Critchley, JA, Garner, P, Sinclair, D, Olliaro, PL, Bhutta, ZA|title=Fluoroquinolones for treating typhoid and paratyphoid fever (enteric fever). |journal=Cochrane database of systematic reviews (Online)|date=2011-10-05|issue=10|pages=CD004530|pmid=21975746|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD004530.pub4}}</ref>和贾第鞭毛虫等。<ref name=Giar2010/>在贾第鞭毛虫或痢疾阿米巴感染时，[[替硝唑|替硝唑]]优于甲硝唑，是首选治疗药物。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Gonzales|first=ML|coauthors=Dans, LF, Martinez, EG|title=Antiamoebic drugs for treating amoebic colitis. |journal=Cochrane database of systematic reviews (Online)|date=2009-04-15|issue=2|pages=CD006085|pmid=19370624|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD006085.pub2}}</ref><ref name=Giar2010/>[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]（ＷＨＯ）建议对同时有便血和发烧的小儿应使用抗生素。<ref name=EBMED2010/>

===止泻药物===
止泻药物在理论上有并发症的风险，虽然临床经验表明这种可能性不大，<ref name="Oxford"/>在便血或伴有发烧的腹泻情况下不建议使用。<ref name="Harrison">{{cite book |title=Harrison's Principles of Internal Medicine |publisher=McGraw-Hill |isbn=0-07-140235-7 |edition=16th |url=http://books.mcgraw-hill.com/medical/harrisons/ |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120804162006/http://books.mcgraw-hill.com/medical/harrisons/ |archivedate=2012-08-04 }}</ref>[[洛哌丁胺|洛哌丁胺]]是一种[[阿片|阿片]]类似物，常用于腹泻的对症治疗。<ref name="SleisengerFordtran">{{cite book |first1=Mark |last1=Feldman |first2=Lawrence S. |last2=Friedman |first3=Marvin H. |last3=Sleisenger |title=Sleisenger & Fordtran's Gastrointestinal and Liver Disease |publisher=Saunders |year=2002 |isbn=0-7216-8973-6 |edition=7th |url=http://www.elsevier-international.com/catalogue/title.cfm?ISBN=0721689736 |access-date=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2007-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927214413/http://www.elsevier-international.com/catalogue/title.cfm?ISBN=0721689736 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>但是洛派丁胺不适于用于儿童，因为此药物可能会穿越儿童尚未成熟的血脑屏障，引起中毒。[[水杨酸亚铋|水杨酸亚铋]]是一种不溶的三价[[铋|铋]]和水杨酸复合物，可以在轻至中度病例中使用，<ref name="Oxford"/>但在理论上[[水杨酸中毒|水杨酸中毒]]是可能的。<ref name=EBMED2010/>

