据计全球每年有三亿到五亿胃肠炎病例，<ref>{{cite journal|last=Elliott|first=EJ|title=Acute gastroenteritis in children. |journal=BMJ (Clinical research ed. )|date=2007-01-06|volume=334|issue=7583|pages=35–40|pmid=17204802|doi=10.1136/bmj.39036.406169.80|pmc = 1764079}}</ref>主要发生于[[发展中世界|发展中世界]]的儿童中。<ref name=Web09/>在2008年有1.3亿五岁以下儿童死于胃肠炎，<ref>{{cite journal|last=Black|first=RE|coauthors=Cousens, S, Johnson, HL, Lawn, JE, Rudan, I, Bassani, DG, Jha, P, Campbell, H, Walker, CF, Cibulskis, R, Eisele, T, Liu, L, Mathers, C, Child Health Epidemiology Reference Group of WHO and, UNICEF|title=Global, regional, and national causes of child mortality in 2008: a systematic analysis. |journal=Lancet|date=2010-06-05|volume=375|issue=9730|pages=1969–87|pmid=20466419|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(10)60549-1}}</ref>大多数这些死亡病例发生在世界上最贫穷的国家中。<ref name=M93/>这些死亡病例中有多于45万是患小儿轮状病毒的5岁以下的幼童。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Tate|first=JE|coauthors=Burton, AH, Boschi-Pinto, C, Steele, AD, Duque, J, Parashar, UD, WHO-coordinated Global Rotavirus Surveillance, Network|title=2008 estimate of worldwide rotavirus-associated mortality in children younger than 5 years before the introduction of universal rotavirus vaccination programmes: a systematic review and meta-analysis. |journal=The Lancet infectious diseases|date=2012 Feb|volume=12|issue=2|pages=136–41|pmid=22030330|doi=10.1016/S1473-3099(11)70253-5}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=World Health Organization|title=Global networks for surveillance of rotavirus gastroenteritis, 2001–2008|journal=Weekly Epidemiological Record|volume=47|issue=83|pages=421–428|url=http://www.who.int/wer/2008/wer8347.pdf|accessdate=10 May 2012|date=November 2008|archive-date=2012-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120709014120/http://www.who.int/wer/2008/wer8347.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>每年有三百万到五百万[[霍乱|霍乱]]病例，引起10万病例死亡。<ref name=Cholera11/>在发展中国家的两岁以下儿童常每年感染六次或更多临床意义上的胃肠炎。<ref name=M93/>成年人的感染较为少见，部分原因是后天获得的[[免疫（医学）|免疫]]。<ref name=Eck2011/>

在1980年，由各种原因导致的肠胃炎造成了460万儿童的死亡，绝大多数发生在发展中国家。<ref name="Mandell">{{cite book |first1=Gerald L. |last1=Mandell |first2=John E. |last2=Bennett |first3=Raphael |last3=Dolin |title=Mandell's Principles and Practices of Infection Diseases |publisher=Churchill Livingstone |year=2004 |isbn=0-443-06643-4 |edition=6th |url=http://www.ppidonline.com |access-date=2020-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180730170741/http://www.ppidonline.com/ |archive-date=2018-07-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>到2000年，死亡率明显减少（每年约150万人死亡），主要是由于[[口服补液治疗|口服补液治疗]]的引进和广泛使用。<ref name="Victora2000">{{cite journal |author=Victora CG, Bryce J, Fontaine O, Monasch R |title=Reducing deaths from diarrhoea through oral rehydration therapy |journal=Bull. World Health Organ. |volume=78|issue=10 |pages=1246–55 |year=2000 |pmid=11100619 |pmc=2560623}}</ref>在美国，引起肠胃炎的感染是名列第二的最常见的感染（仅次于[[普通感冒|普通感冒]]），每年引起2亿到3.75亿急性腹泻<ref name=Eck2011/><ref name=M93/>及大约一万死亡病例，<ref name=M93/>其中有150到300起死亡病例发生在五岁以下的儿童中。<ref name=EBMED2010/>

===历史===
「肠胃炎」这一词语的第一次使用是在1825年。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oed.com/ |title=Gastroenteritis |format= |work=[[Oxford_English_Dictionary|Oxford English Dictionary]] 2011 |accessdate=January 15, 2012 |archive-date=2008-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080111125659/http://www.oed.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在此之前，胃肠炎被称为[[伤寒|伤寒]]、「霍乱寒」，或其他名称，又或含糊地被称为「肠绞痛」、「surfeit」，「flux」，「colic」，「bowel complaint」，或急性腹泻的许多旧称之一。<ref name="archaic">{{Cite web |url=http://www./ |title=antiquusmorbus. com/English/English. htm Rudy's List of Archaic Medical Terms |accessdate=2020-09-17 |archive-date=2007-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071020025208/http://www./ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==社会及文化==
胃肠炎有许多口语化的名称，如“[[墨西哥毒计|墨西哥毒針]]”、“拉德里肚”、“旅游病”、“后门跑”等等。<ref name="M93" />它在很多军队宣传占一席之地，并被认为是英文俗语“no guts no glory”（没有勇气就没有荣耀；guts 意为肚子，也指勇气）的来源。<ref name="M93" />

在美国<ref name=EBMED2010/>每年有370万看诊的主要原因是胃肠炎，在法国这个数字是3百万。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Flahault|first=A|coauthors=Hanslik, T|title=[Epidemiology of viral gastroenteritis in France and Europe]. |journal=Bulletin de l'Academie nationale de medecine|date=2010 Nov|volume=194|issue=8|pages=1415–24; discussion 1424-5|pmid=22046706}}</ref>据信胃肠炎每年在美国造成的损失有23亿美元，<ref>{{cite book|last=Albert|first=edited by Neil S. Skolnik ; associate editor, Ross H.|title=Essential infectious disease topics for primary care|year=2008|publisher=Humana Press|location=Totowa, NJ|isbn=978-1-58829-520-0|pages=66|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=iGUKPeO9-ygC&pg=PA66|access-date=2016-11-04|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016105913/http://books.google.ca/books?id=iGUKPeO9-ygC&pg=PA66|dead-url=no}}</ref>仅由轮状病毒引起的损失每年就有1亿美元。<ref name=EBMED2010/>

==研究==
有一定数量的胃肠炎疫苗正在研发中。例如全球肠胃炎的首要病源之首，志贺菌和肠毒素“大肠埃希氏大肠杆菌”（ETEC）的疫苗。<ref name="WHO ETEC">{{cite web |last=World Health Organization |title=Enterotoxigenic Escherichia coli (ETEC) |url=http://www.who.int/vaccine_research/diseases/diarrhoeal/en/index4.html |work=Diarrhoeal Diseases |accessdate=3 May 2012 |archive-date=2013-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014040247/http://www.who.int/vaccine_research/diseases/diarrhoeal/en/index4.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="WHO Shig">{{cite web |last=World Health Organization |title=Shigellosis |url=http://www.who.int/vaccine_research/diseases/diarrhoeal/en/index6.html |work=Diarrhoeal Diseases |accessdate=3 May 2012 |archive-date=2013-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014091055/http://www.who.int/vaccine_research/diseases/diarrhoeal/en/index6.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==其他动物中的肠胃炎==
许多引起猫狗肠胃炎的病源与人类病源相同。最常见的生物病源为：空肠弯曲菌、艰难梭菌、产气荚膜梭菌和沙门氏菌。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Weese |first=JS |title=Bacterial enteritis in dogs and cats: diagnosis, therapy, and zoonotic potential. |journal=The Veterinary clinics of North America. Small animal practice |date=2011 Mar |volume=41 |issue=2 |pages=287-309 |pmid=21486637 |doi=10.1016/j.cvsm.2010.12.005}}</ref>大量有毒植物也可能会导致胃肠症状。<ref>{{cite book |last=Rousseaux |first=Wanda Haschek, Matthew Wallig, Colin |title=Fundamentals of toxicologic pathology |year=2009 |publisher=Academic |location=London |isbn=9780123704696 |pages=182 |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=vkox3JS83k8C&pg=PA182 |edition=2nd ed. |access-date=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2013-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131226012937/http://books.google.ca/books?id=vkox3JS83k8C&pg=PA182 |dead-url=no }}</ref>一些病源对某些物种有针对性。[[猪传染性胃肠炎冠状病毒|猪传染性胃肠炎冠状病毒]]（猪传染性胃肠炎TGEV）造成猪的呕吐、腹泻和脱水。<ref>{{cite book |last=MacLachlan |first=edited by N. James |title=Fenner's veterinary virology |year=2009 |publisher=Elsevier Academic Press |location=Amsterdam |page=399 |isbn=9780123751584 |edition=4th ed. |coauthors=Dubovi, Edward J. |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=TYFqlYO9eE4C&pg=PA399 |access-date=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2013-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216135953/http://books.google.ca/books?id=TYFqlYO9eE4C&pg=PA399 |dead-url=no }}</ref>据信是由野生鸟传播，并没有特殊的治疗办法。<ref>{{cite book |last=al. ] |first=edited by James G. Fox . . . [et |title=Laboratory animal medicine |year=2002 |publisher=Academic Press |location=Amsterdam |isbn=9780122639517 |pages=649 |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=m2ftfPMJnMMC&pg=PA649 |edition=2nd ed. |access-date=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2013-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216140003/http://books.google.ca/books?id=m2ftfPMJnMMC&pg=PA649 |dead-url=no }}</ref>此病不会传播给人类。<ref>{{cite book |last=al. ] |first=edited by Jeffrey J. Zimmerman . . . [et |title=Diseases of swine |publisher=Wiley-Blackwell |location=Chichester, West Sussex |isbn=9780813822679 |pages=504 |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=jVaemau17J4C&pg=PA504 |edition=10th ed. |access-date=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2013-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131226013058/http://books.google.ca/books?id=jVaemau17J4C&pg=PA504 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

